## VERDICT
Set the top-level `overall_correctness`, `overall_explanation`, and `overall_confidence_score` fields based on the merged finding list and reviewer verdicts.
"patch is correct" means the patch is free of blocking issues and should not break existing code or tests.
Otherwise return "patch is incorrect".

